title: Notwithstanding anything contained in any Government Order, Government Resolution, Government Notification, etc
clause_text: Notwithstanding anything contained in any Government Order, Government Resolution, Government Notification, etc. issued from time to time regarding powers of relaxation in Development Control and Promotional regulations, the above provision shall prevail.
